      <scopecontent id="aspace_409a7a6891d7b612b94c20e5f8f14f93">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of postcards, correspondence, and notes documenting the 25th reunion of the Yale College Class of 1924. Also included is a videotaped interview with Ray Daniels, a member of the class.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
